<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../Home/home.css">
   
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><b>Welcome to our TRAVIGO!</b></h1>
        <p>Plan your next trip with us and get ready for an unforgettable experience.</p>
        <a href="/listings" class="but" >Plan Your Trip</a>
        <a href="/solotrip" class="but" >Solo Trip?</a>
        
        <div class="images-wrapper">
            <img class="travel" src="../Home/home_icon.jpg" alt="Travel">
            <img class="plane" src="../Home/plane.jpg" alt="Plane">
        </div>
        
        <div class="about">
            <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
            <p>At TRAVIGO, we're passionate about simplifying your travel experience. Our AI-powered platform takes the hassle out of planning and booking your trips by providing personalized recommendations tailored to your preferences. Whether you're seeking adventure, relaxation, or cultural exploration, we're here to make your travel dreams a reality. Join us and discover the future of travel planning today.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="container2"> 
            <h1 class="features-heading">FEATURES</h1>
            <div class="feature border-style">
                <h2>Tailored Suggestions</h2>
                <p>Our AI-powered platform analyzes your preferences and past trips to offer personalized recommendations tailored to your interests.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature  border-style">
                <h2>Integration with Popular Travel Services</h2>
                <p>Seamlessly connect with popular travel services such as airlines, hotels, and car rentals to streamline your travel experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature border-style">
                <h2>Easy booking process</h2>
                <p>Our intuitive interface makes booking your next trip a breeze. With just a few clicks, you can select your destination, choose your accommodations, and finalize your itinerary without any hassle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature border-style">
                <h2>24/7 customer support</h2>
                <p>Rest assured knowing that our dedicated support team is available around the clock to assist you with any queries or concerns you may have. Whether it's help with booking, changes to your itinerary, or emergency assistance during your travels, we're here to ensure your peace of mind.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature  border-style">
                <h2>Secure payment options</h2>
                <p>Your payment security is our top priority. We offer a range of secure payment options, including credit card, PayPal, and more, to ensure that your financial information remains safe and protected throughout the booking process.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Guest Reviews</h2>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="review-info">
                <img src="../Home/avatar1.jpg" alt="Avatar" class="avatar">
                <div class="review-text">
                    <p><strong>Jasmine Doe</strong></p>
                    <p>"I had an amazing experience with TRAVIGO! The recommendations were spot on, and the booking process was effortless."</p>
                    <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="review-info">
                <img src="../Home/avatar2.jpg" alt="Avatar" class="avatar">
                <div class="review-text">
                    <p><strong>Jane Smith</strong></p>
                    <p>"TRAVIGO made my vacation planning stress-free. I highly recommend it to anyone looking for a seamless travel experience."</p>
                    <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>        

        <!-- Other Sections -->
        <!-- You can add more sections here as needed -->

    </div>
</body>
</html>
